{"tid":2027156,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【歷史台】繁華但躁動不安的城市—1960年代的滿地可(蒙特利爾)","createTime":"2020-05-21T10:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T13:07:35.000Z","uid":120678,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3c64fda4793967128afc2b1abf29049ac35ff4c4","tid":2027156,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/484083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprime.fortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F484083&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVzeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=470e5bc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/484083</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/7880753798_e60c4f455b_b-500x263.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprime.fortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F7880753798_e60c4f455b_b-500x263.jpg&h=ec541fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由16世紀初法國派探險家橫跨大西洋到達北美的東岸開始，我呢個post提到法國點樣殖民北美洲、點樣失去北美洲既殖民地、英國統治下加拿大既種族矛盾問題、加拿大聯邦的成立、兩次大戰之間英法裔因徵兵令引起既衝突，時間終於來到左20世紀中葉、戰後的魁北克。<br />\n<br />\n可能大家未必知，小弟既故鄉其實正正就係魁北克的最大城市&mdash;&mdash;滿地可(蒙特利爾)，呢座城市響香港唔係好出名，但如果大家有留意本港樂壇，香港黃絲民主女神何韻詩都曾經響滿地可住過(仲出過一首同名歌曲)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。小弟有幸同佢住過同一座城市，不過我直頭響果度出世，而我出世時正正就係魁北克獨立運動火紅火熱的年代。不過呢篇文章要回帶返去呢個年代(80s末期)之前，我未出世既時代，去追尋魁獨運動既根源。<br />\n<br />\n1960年代，滿地可曾經係加拿大最大既城市，比多倫多仲要大、人口更多，經濟亦都十分繁榮。距今近60年前既時代，滿地可係歐洲人進入加拿大的門戶城市，整座城市大興土木、修橋鋪路、建造大量新地鐵線、修建全加拿大最大既新機場、甚至主辦世博會，整座城市充滿左活力。響呢度，優秀既大學培養出頂尖既人才，高新科技工業例如飛機製造得以發展。但繁榮的表面背後，係深刻既種族矛盾&mdash;&mdash;講英文既英裔掌控左全省全城既經濟命脈，講法文既法裔感覺被排除在外。誇張d講：英裔住響皇家山附近既豪宅區，樓價當時全加拿大最貴，法裔就響農場收集楓糖。正正係呢個背景之下，魁北克獨立的風暴正悄悄醞釀&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n另外提提大家，小弟係Fortune Insight雜誌專欄作家。如果鍾意我既文章，可以考慮以訂閱的方式打賞小弟。下面呢個link有我響FI Prime出過既文章，新文章逢週四刊出，再次感謝大家既支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/author/zannanza-hattusili\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprime.fortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2Fauthor%2Fzannanza-hattusili&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVzeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=25064da5\" target=\"_blank\">https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/author/zannanza-hattusili</a><br />\n<br />\n前兩個post：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1999026/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1999026/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2016117/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2016117/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n最後再宣傳下小弟響社交網站SNS既專頁<br />\n小弟FB page，專講古典世史：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/zannanza\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fzannanza&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVzeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=008be5ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/zannanza</a><br />\nTwitter(面向國際讀者，所以內容全英，希望唔好介意)：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/zannanzahistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fzannanzahistory&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVzeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=8af9a19e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/zannanzahistory</a>"},{"pid":"3db3b3186ed3b3f393db8f06c33c9faba85f2428","tid":2027156,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea01eb2293aa34cb99847085cb81699607eda137","tid":2027156,"uid":47593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:38:05.000Z","msg":"推，巴打加油"},{"pid":"2ce21f696f9954585eda4fee314a2e6e8fad6f5d","tid":2027156,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"815ba0dc45ac3ee904471c1a3140fa65ac07d287","tid":2027156,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:17:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ba5acd6c97dac4af921ab51b1dcb20b96d4702ce","tid